#~ msgid ""
#~ "We met at our university camp in 2018 - we were finishing each other's "
#~ "sentences, laughing way too much, and somehow already acting like we'd "
#~ "known each other for years. Also, it turns out that being fed is, in "
#~ "fact, a very effective love language - and one of us was completely won "
#~ "over. Since then, we've been on countless adventures, collected a lot of "
#~ "memories (and probably did a few questionable travel decisions), and "
#~ "eventually built a home together - which still feels a bit unreal and "
#~ "very us. And now, here we are, starting our next chapter. Having you here "
#~ "means everything to us. Some of you witnessed the very beginning, others "
#~ "joined somewhere along the way - but all of you are part of this story. "
#~ "We feel so lucky to celebrate it together with you."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ми познайомилися в університетському таборі у 2018 році - ми закінчували "
